97
00:09:57,527 --> 00:09:58,528
Di sisiku.

98
00:10:03,658 --> 00:10:04,575
Mari kita pergi.

99
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:09,789
Aku tak kedinginan.

100
00:10:09,872 --> 00:10:12,208
Bukan itu alasanku memakaikan ini.

101
00:10:13,042 --> 00:10:14,794
Selatan tempat yang mengerikan.

102
00:10:14,877 --> 00:10:17,505
Banyak kamera pengawas,
kamera dasbor, dan ponsel.

103
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:19,590
Juga koneksi internet tercepat di dunia.

104
00:10:19,674 --> 00:10:21,092
Jika wajahmu terlihat,

105
00:10:21,175 --> 00:10:23,386
