Kita bisa pesan.
Bilang saja mau makan apa.

144
00:12:55,162 --> 00:12:57,206
Piza? Masakan Tionghoa?

145
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:58,207
Atau ayam goreng?

146
00:12:59,625 --> 00:13:02,962
