restoran ayam goreng di Selatan?

147
00:13:04,672 --> 00:13:06,090
Banyak orang makan ayam.

148
00:13:08,843 --> 00:13:10,177
Aku ingin tahu harganya.

149
00:13:10,761 --> 00:13:14,307
