203
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,072
Dia hanya mengabaikannya.

204
00:16:58,864 --> 00:17:00,157
Aku tahu sandinya.

205
00:17:01,117 --> 00:17:02,118
Tekanlah.

206
00:17:07,998 --> 00:17:09,667
Kau yakin keamanannya ketat?

207
00:17:09,750 --> 00:17:13,462
Masuklah ke kamar, dan bawa jaketmu.

208
00:17:15,423 --> 00:17:16,424
