209
00:17:19,844 --> 00:17:22,513
Kalian sedang apa?
Ini bisa dianggap penerobosan.

210
00:17:22,596 --> 00:17:25,182
Sudahlah. Aku kakakmu.

211
00:17:25,266 --> 00:17:28,102
- Hei, dari mana...
- Kenapa telepon kami diblokir?

212
00:17:28,185 --> 00:17:29,728
Kata siapa boleh masuk?

213
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:42,533
