Ini peringatan terakhir.

278
00:21:26,674 --> 00:21:27,508
Jangan...

279
00:21:28,926 --> 00:21:31,345
mengatakan apa pun.

280
00:21:32,971 --> 00:21:34,556
Aku terlalu malu.

281
00:21:36,475 --> 00:21:37,810
Aku tak akan bicara.

282
00:21:57,204 --> 00:21:58,288
Ini lebih baik.

283
00:21:59,832 --> 00:22:01,291
Hening.

284
00:22:03,335 --> 00:22:04,545
Dan hangat.

285
00:22:05,254 --> 00:22:06,505
Entah kenapa...

286
00:22:08,173 --> 00:22:09,591
ini meredakan amarahku.

287
00:22:10,634 --> 00:22:12,261
Tapi aku kesal.

288
00:22:13,429 --> 00:22:16,348
Aku sangat kesal sampai hampir lupa
dengan situasiku sendiri.

289
00:22:25,858 --> 00:22:26,859
Tapi...

290
00:22:29,069 --> 00:22:30,112
jangan lupa

291
