Gwang Beom,

352
00:26:46,827 --> 00:26:49,538
mungkin dia berikan semuanya
karena kau tampan.

353
00:26:50,455 --> 00:26:53,375
Kalau begitu, aku harus coba.

354
00:26:55,085 --> 00:26:56,169
Mari makan.

355
00:26:58,422 --> 00:26:59,548
Terima kasih.

356
