385
00:29:07,092 --> 00:29:08,426
Aku juga.

386
00:29:09,469 --> 00:29:12,139
Omong-omong, apakah peramal itu hebat?

387
00:29:13,223 --> 00:29:14,599
Dia hebat.

388
00:29:14,683 --> 00:29:17,227
Lima tahun terakhir,
dia meramal soal promosi suamiku,

389
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,687
